{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/android-keyboard-up/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>안드로이드 <strong>액티비티가 전환</strong>될 때 <strong><code class=\"language-text\">edit text</code>에 키보드가 바로 뜨게</strong> 해보자!</p>\n<h2 id=\"방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>방법</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>edit text 에 focus 해주기\n액티비티가 전환되자마자 키보드가 올라와있게 하는 목적은 <strong>사용자가 edt에 바로 입력할 수 있게 하기 위해서</strong>다! 따라서 edt에 focus가 되어있지 않으면 의미가 없다.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">EditText</span> searchEdt <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">findViewById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">R</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>id<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>edt_search<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nsearchEdt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">requestFocus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">requestFocus()</code> 를 이용해서 포커스를 해줫다.</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>키보드 올리기</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">InputMethodManager</span> imm <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">InputMethodManager</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token function\">getSystemService</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>INPUT_METHOD_SERVICE<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nimm<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toggleSoftInput</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">InputMethodManager</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>SHOW_FORCED<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">InputMethodManager</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>HIDE_IMPLICIT_ONLY<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>다음으로 이 코드를 넣어준다!</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>이렇게 되면, 키보드는 올라와 있고, focus가 지정해 준 edt가 되므로 edt에 글자를 쓸 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"출처\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EC%B2%98\" aria-label=\"출처 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출처</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://alaveiw.tistory.com/133\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://alaveiw.tistory.com/133</a></p>","excerpt":"안드로이드 액티비티가 전환될 때 에 키보드가 바로 뜨게 해보자! 방법 edit text 에 focus 해주기\n액티비티가 전환되자마자 키보드가 올라와있게